Recommends: libgl1
Description: Interactive post-processing tool for scanned pages
 Scan Tailor is an interactive post-processing tool for scanned pages.
 It performs operations such as page splitting, deskewing, adding/removing
 borders, and selecting content. It supports batch processing and can
 output to TIFF, PNG or JPEG.
 .
 This package provides both the graphical application (scantailor) and
 the command-line batch tool (scantailor-cli).
